thing: `registerStep` pushes to `globalSteps`. So every time `autoBindSteps` is 
called, MORE steps are added to `globalSteps`. This means `globalSteps` grows mo
notonically.\n\nFor the auth test, `globalSteps` should contain:\n1. All steps f
rom `common.js` (registered when previous BDD tests ran)\n2. All steps from `aut
h-common.js` (registered when the auth test runs)\n\nSo there should be plenty o
