e: () => true })\n    .compile();\n```\n\nThe `AuthModule` imports `TypeOrmModul
e.forFeature([UserEntity, UserProfileEntity])`. When we override the provider, i
t should work. But `getServer()` returns `{ server, mockRedis: mockRedisMethods,
userRepo, profileRepo }`.\n\nWait, but in the first call to `getServer()`, the `
